}{\plain \fs24 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b 64.}{\plain \fs24   M. Barbi (}{\plain \fs24 \i Problemi di critica dantesca}{\plain \fs24  [Florence: Sansoni, 1934]), p. 261: }{\plain \fs24 \i sciaurati}{\plain \fs24  \softline
must be understood as 'vile, abbietto, da niente,' as a bitterly negative term with no softness in it.  \softline
